nodes.text: Joth Katrane was a male Human from Corellia who was present at Desolation Alley during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. In 32 BBY, he was wanted by someone who cheated him out of his pension by reporting his 'extra' income to the warden. Eventually, his bounty was claimed by the Mandalorian-turned Bounty hunter named Jango Fett.
Joth Katrane's bounty is 6,000 credits alive and 3,000 credits dead.
